"Centang kotakcentang <guilabel>Tampilkan video</guilabel> untuk membolehkan "
"&gwenview; menampilkan video di antara citra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Only during slideshows</guilabel> item if notifications "
"about reaching the list end should be shown only in <link linkend="
"\"fullscreen\">the slideshow mode</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Always</guilabel> item if you want to receive the "
"notifications unconditionally."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background color"
msgstr "Warna latarbelakang"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move the slider to change the color of the gray background in Browse and "
"View mode from black (the leftmost position) to white (the rightmost "
"position)."
msgstr ""
"Gerakkan penggeser untuk mengubah warna pada latarbelakang abu di dalam mode "
"Telusur dan Tampilan dari hitam (posisi paling kiri) ke putih (posisi paling "
"kanan)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:723
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Full Screen Modes"
msgid "Fullscreen background"
msgstr "Mode Layar Penuh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:727
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Browse</guilabel> &mdash; Switch to the next or the previous "
#| "image."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Black</guilabel> &mdash; Set the background color in fullscreen "
"mode to black."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Telusur</guilabel> &mdash; Beralih ke citra selanjutnya atau "
"sebelumnya."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Dark gray texture</guilabel> &mdash; Set the background in "
"fullscreen mode to a dark gray texture."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:736
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "JPEG save quality"
msgid "Lossy image save quality"
msgstr "Kualitas penyimpanan JPEG"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "JPEG save/compression quality setting, which can be temporarily "
#| "overridden in the <guilabel>Save As</guilabel> dialog when saving a file "
#| "as a JPEG. When saving an existing JPEG file with a new name or after "
#| "performing a non-lossy edit (&eg; rotation, which only changes the EXIF "
#| "rotation tag), the appearance of the file is not changed because no "
#| "actual image manipulation is done."
msgid ""
"Save/compression quality setting for lossy image formats like JPEG, WEBP, "
"AVIF, HEIF, and HEIC, which can be temporarily overridden in the "
"<guilabel>Save As</guilabel> dialog when saving a file in a lossy image "
"format. When saving an existing lossy image with a new name or after "
"performing a non-lossy edit (&eg; rotation, which only changes the EXIF "
"rotation tag), the appearance of the file is not changed because no actual "
"image manipulation is done."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan kualitas penyimpanan/kompresi JPEG, yang bisa ditimpa secara "
"temporer di dalam dialog <guilabel>Simpan Sebagai</guilabel> ketika "
"menyimpan file sebagai JPEG. Ketika menyimpan file JPEG yang ada dengan nama "
"baru atau setelah melakukan pengeditan yang tidak hilang (&eg; perotasian, "
"yang hanya mengubah tag rotasi EXIF), penampilan file tidak berubah karena "
"tidak ada manipulasi citra yang sebenarnya dilakukan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thumbnail actions"
msgstr "Aksi gambar-mini"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether the thumbnail action buttons should be shown as overlays above image "
"thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Apakah tombol aksi gambar-mini harus ditampilkan sewaktu melayang di atas "
"citra gambar-mini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>All buttons</guilabel> &mdash; Show all buttons"
msgstr "<guilabel>Semua tombol</guilabel> &mdash; Tampilkan semua tombol"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show selection button only</guilabel> &mdash; Show select/unselect "
"button only"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tampilkan tombol pemilihan saja</guilabel> &mdash; Tampilkan "
"tombol pilih/takpilih saja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>None</guilabel> &mdash; Do not show any thumbnail button"
